==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Chit
<hw>Chit</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To shoot out; to sprout.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I have known barley <qex>chit</qex> in seven hours after it had
been thrown forth.</q> <rj><qau>Mortimer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

